{"tid":672640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鐘意左個有男朋友嘅女仔","createTime":"2018-05-21T07:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T08:13:22.000Z","uid":148703,"like":0,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ab4de214c015d9061925009ac823add20d419c","tid":672640,"uid":148703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:35:22.000Z","msg":"如題，點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n控制唔到自己唔去諗<br />\n近來一星期夢見佢兩三日<br />\n想她想得好孤寂，好辛苦<br />\n我有主動搵佢whatsapp，佢都會認我<br />\n感覺都係普通朋友對話，無乜曖昧<br />\n試過約佢單獨食個飯，佢又答應<br />\n不過未到個日，好緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n知道佢男朋友好似對馬馬地，好少見<br />\n成日掛住番工唔理佢<br />\n自問自己package唔錯，應該好過佢條仔<br />\n<br />\n如果你係我，你會點？<br />\n第一次食飯應唔應該表白或對佢暗示有好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c23d41d80741f994095b612f44f15f257cb37fe","tid":672640,"uid":134487,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:36:13.000Z","msg":"返屋企打飛機啦 死狗公"},{"pid":"156e01ee8ce01b90e99945d35e056fc07f5b7223","tid":672640,"uid":78971,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:36:25.000Z","msg":"你搶到咪搶囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最怕你連個朋友都冇埋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ecdaaf71238e3f9d9b54e1500ffd889e8a7f73","tid":672640,"uid":148703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c23d41d80741f994095b612f44f15f257cb37fe","tid":672640,"uid":134487,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:36:13.000Z","msg":"返屋企打飛機啦 死狗公"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"我認真架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89322b999585a570ff34969b875da3f34f6efa47","tid":672640,"uid":134487,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c8ecdaaf71238e3f9d9b54e1500ffd889e8a7f73","tid":672640,"uid":148703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"